Ilul deg walef uttseε meyya usetta urebεin, di Agadu, deg yirebbi n yidurar n Neffusa, anẓul-amalu n tmurt n Libya n wass-a.
D ayen i t-iḥettmen ad yuɣal ɣer Trablus deg walef uttseε meyya usebεa usettin, ad iɣer azref, anda i d-iḥella agerdas n ubugaṭu.
Seg umezruy, ass n xemseṭṭac yunyu zuǧ alaf uttesεa, ugin yimḍebbren n tmurt n Merruk ad d-yettwasken i tɣamsa Udlis aberkan n Saɛid Sifaw deg Uqusis n Tɣamsa n Rribaṭ.
Yella ussan-a iɛeddan di Bgayet unemhal amatu n Uxxam aɣelnaw n yizerfan n umeskar d yizerfan inaragen Mass Sami Bencix, i lmend n usarag i d-iga deg usensu Crystal.
Mi d-yesmekta inaẓuren ɣef wazal n uḥuddu n yisnulfuyen-nsen sɣur Uxxam aɣelnaw n yizerfan n umeskar d yizerfan inaragen, yenna-d unemhal-is belli ihegga ad yesbedd di Bgayet aɣerbaz n tẓuriwin ɣer sdat, abeɛda ma ur d-mlalen ugur deg tifin n unnar anda ara yettwabnu.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken aṭas n tlufa iɣef i d-yemmeslay iseggasen-a ineggura unemhal ɣef wayen yerzan aqader n yizerfan n umeskar.
Ama d aẓawan neɣ d tugna, yenna-d Mass Bencix ilaq fell-asent ad ttxellisent izerfan n umeskar, akken ur yettili ccɣel d tukerḍa n uzref n unaẓur.
Dima deg ubrid n uḥuddu ɣef unaẓur d usnulfu n wallaɣ, isuter unemhal amatu n yizerfan n umeskar ula d takebbanit tameqqrant Google akken ad d-tettak izerfan i yinaẓuren i yesrusuyen di Youtube iqeddicen-nsen n tẓuri.
Xas ulamma tenna-d tneɣlaft n tjara d akken ssumat n lxuḍra, lfakya akked uksum ad subbent, maca deg unnar, nettwali d ayen-nniḍen i iḍerrun.
Ma yella wid teɛna temsalt di lwilaya, ilaq fell-asen ad d-ffɣen akken ad ɛassen wigi ixeddmen leswami akken i d asen-yehwa acku di yal tamnadt amek ara tent-tafeḍ, ur ɛdilent ara”.
Ma d aseqqamu-agi i bɣan ad sbedden d aleqqem d usejhed n yimenzayen n tɣamsa i d-yebder usaḍuf agmanan n uselɣu, i d-yeffɣen deg useggas n zuǧ alaf utnac.
Asuddis addalan n xemsin alef n yimukan n Tizi Uzzu, i d-tesfaydi terbaɛt n yilmeẓyen n Leqbayel, ad d-yewjed deg wakud i as-d-yettuɛeggnen,di taggara n waggur n ɣuct i d-iteddun.
Iberreḥ s waya, lwali n Tizi Uzzu Meḥmud Ǧemεa, i yerzan ɣur-s taggara n ddurt iɛeddan, anida i yessefqed aswir uɣur wwḍen lecɣal n usenfar-agi.
Ad d-nesmekti kan belli, deg waggur n meɣres iɛeddan i srekben yakan xemsin alef n yikersiwen n yimferǧen n unnar-agi meqqren, i d-igren s annar taluft n yisem-is.
Ma d aselway n terbaɛt n yelmezyen n Leqbayel, Crif Mellal, yemtawa d umsulɣu Guillaume Mulak iwakken ad yili d anemhal n usileɣ deg wammas n usileɣ n terbaɛt-agi.
D Guillaume Mulak ara d-yelhin s usileɣ n yimurar ilmeẓyen ara d-tettrebbi terbaɛt-agi n yilmeẓyen n Leqbayel deg wammas anaddal, ara yilin deg tama n Wad Ɛisi.
Tettwaselmed di lakul akken i tt-ssarmen yimeɣnasen n tmanyin, gar-asen Dda Lmulud, maca mačči s lekmal, acku yewwi-d ad tettwasɣar deg yakk tamurt.
Ass n letnayen iεeddan, ttesεa uεecrin deg wagur n yebrir, i yenɣa iman-is yiwen n yilemẓi n sebεa uεecrin n yiseggasen, n taddart n At Ḥmed i ibeεden s sin n yikilumitren ɣef tlemmast n tɣiwant n Mεatqa.
Deg wass-nni n letnayen ɣef lewhi n tmeddit i yufan yemsebriden ilemẓi-agi yenɣa iman-is s tmuxniqt, deg umḍiq n Buḥemdun, anda yuɣ tannumi yettɣama d imeddukkal-is, yerna yexdem addal.
Ccnawi d yisuɣan s ṭṭelq n yijaɣuɣen akked wallus n kra n tezlatin tigrawliwin, llant tezlatin n Maɛtub (Ḥzen am leɛyun), Uleḥlu (Iǧadermiyen akked pouvoir assassin), Ali Ideflawen (Ǧǧet-iyi abrid ad ɛeddiɣ).
Gar wayen nezmer ad d-nɣer deg twerqtin-nni n usuter, d wagi : « Tamurt ur tettaf ixef-is alamma tufa aẓar-is », « Ad nennaɣ alamma yeɣli udabu ».
D wid ifernen wid ara yilin kan i yeẓran amek fernen, anwi i d isefranen-nsen, ayɣer wwin win wwin, ayɣer ǧǧan wid ǧǧan.
imi ssawḍen kra n yimetjaren ibeznasen n wakal ad gezmen ugar n mitin n ṭṭjur deg yiwet n teẓgi iwumi ssawalen Kuka, i d-yezgan ɣer tama n lfirma Xmisti.
Tarbaɛt-a, i usmekti, ttekkin deg-s tmanya n yimdanen, mbeɛd mi ara ḥewṣen leqwaɛi, ttqeɛɛiden akal, ttarran-d ayla-nsen, syin snuzuyen-t akken d imersunen neɣ tikwal bennun kra n yixxamen yeffɣen i usaḍuf akken ad sen-ɛiwden lbiɛ i kra seg wid yesran i tnezduɣin s tɣawla.
Mebla ccek, aɣerbaz d aɣbalu amenzu n ddunit ideg amdan, akken yebɣu yili uẓayer-ines, d argaz neɣ d tameṭṭut, d aẓawali neɣ d amerkanti, d aberkan neɣ d acebḥan… yessefk ad d-iɛeddi fell-as, ad d-yagem timussniwin, yis-sent ad yezger talsa, ad yessiweḍ ayen i d-yegmer d wayen yessen ɣer tsuta i d-yettasen d win ur nessin ara, akka i iteddu wakud.
Aɣerbaz d aḥric am waṭas n yiḥricen deg tudert n umdan, ɣur-s talliyin, yal yiwet s tulmisin-is, s wacu i d-tufrar, d acu i d amaynut i swayes i d-tgellu, dacu i d-yerna win yellan fell-as uneɣlaf n usedwel).
Zik, aqcic, yeqqar i yiman-is akken ad yerbeḥ ikayaden-is, ur as-fkan ara tallelt yimawlan-is, acku ur stufan ara, wa tecɣeb-it ddunit, wa yettazzal deffir n uɣrum.
Maca ma nerra lwelha ɣer wahil n uɣerbaz amenzu ɣur-neɣ, ad naf, amedya deg uswir wis ukkuẓ, anelmad yeqqar ilmuden ẓẓayen ɣef uswir-is am umezruy, tarakalt, tasreḍt d tussna.
Maca akken ad yettwagdel ɣef uselmad ula d asuɣu s uwellih ɣef unelmad ara ixedmen tabannaḍt, ayagi yerna tilelli i yinelmaden ad beɛden acemma ɣef ulmud.
Aya iɣef i d-nenna ɣef tuɣalin n uẓayer n uselmad ɣer deffir, ur aɣ-yettagi ara ad d-nini belli llan kra n yiselmaden ur nxeddem ara amahil-nsen akken ilaq, ceɣben-ten lecɣal-nniḍen ɛlaḥsab n tmussni n unelmad.
Deg yiwen n yisalli i d-tessuffeɣ Tuddsa tagraɣlant i uḥraz n ugama, yedda-d kra n umḍan n yiɣersiwen, n umenẓaw n Tefriqt abeɛda, i yellan ɣef yimi n nnger.
Deg wahil-a ara yettwaselḥun sɣur SOS, ad naf iswi amenzu d aseḥbes ulamma cwiṭ n tmettant n yizmawen, iɣilasen, iḍebɛiwen, iḍan n lexla d wuccanen ityupyanen, i simmal ttenṭerrayen seg useyyed berra i usaḍuf, annerni n tnezduɣin d ukcam n yimdanen di tẓegwa.
S tedrimt-a n Tseqqamut turufant, yezmer ad d-yawi kra n ubaɣur usenfar-a n uḥraz iwumi fkan azwel SOS Tiẓgi taferkant.
Ɣef wawal-is, ad yekki daɣ wahil-a deg uḥraz d usellek n kra n yiɣersiwen imehhazen n Tferka i iteddun ad negren, am nutni am yiɣersiwen igemrawen.
Akkin i usenfar-a, yewwi-d ad d-nesmekti d akken, ɣas ma tikwal yesmurrus wahil n uḥraz i d-yettwaskarayen deg Tferka, mazal nnger yeṭṭafar ddeqs n yisenfan n yiɣersiwen, armi drus i d-yeqqimen seg-sen.
Dɣa, deg yiḍ n ttesεa uεecrin ar tlatin yebrir yezrin ɣef rebεa qel sebεa ddqayeq n tnezzayt, iqeddacen n uḥuddu aɣarim, seld asiwel n yiwen n umdan i asen-d-yessutren ad ruḥen s tazzla ɣer tlemmast n temdint n Ticci, anda i yeḍṛa usehwu-a, uzzlen s uɣiwel ɣeṛ umḍiq-nni.






















